    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（よし、スケジュールの調整はバッチリだな）\n（けどこれは、年末のライブに向けて忙しくなるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Alright‚ the schedule is perfectly adjusted.)\n(But this is going to get busy for the year-end live.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7807195028,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5285.947163899999,
          "startTime": 10.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、ちょうど良かった\n今日のスケジュールについてなんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ it's good that I caught you.\nI wanted to talk to you about today's schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "ここ数日、レッスンばかりだよね？\n何か他に仕事って入ってないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've been focused on lessons these past few days‚ right?\nIs there anything else scheduled besides that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、特に今のところは何も……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ not really‚ nothing at the moment…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……いや、それならそれでいいんだ\nじゃ、レッスンに行ってくるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Well‚ if that's the case‚ it's fine.\nI'll be heading to my lesson then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.6666672398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ alright…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1066.6666667000015,
          "startTime": 34.9666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（さすが年末だ。忙し過ぎて体が足りないな）\n（ 事務作業をさばいたら、レッスンの付き添いに……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As expected‚ it's getting hectic towards the year-end.)\n(After handling office work‚ it's time for lesson support…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3399.9999999999986,
          "startTime": 47.9333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "君はなんだか、いつもバタバタしているね\n僕達よりもやることが多そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You always seem so busy.\nIt looks like you have more to do than us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、葵？　どうして……\n今日はボーカルレッスンだったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ Aoi? Why are you…\nToday was supposed to be vocal lessons‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_05_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだけど、もっと他に大事な用事があってね\nこっそり抜け出してきた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it was‚ but I have something more important to do.\nI snuck away for this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
